channel.title: [508] Need help with my 508. [508]
channel.description:
Alright, so I got my source running which is ZuberZoft, no problem. I open a i.p changer for 508's and it goes. I put 0.0.0.0 for the i.p. So it loads up and I type in my user and pass, Than it says error connecting to server, so I try again and it says, "Connection timed out. Please try using a diffrent world." So I reload the client and the same thing happens over and over again. I am such a noob, and would love if anyone helped me, thanks.
~Kaligrok
